etomica.space1d

Class Tensor1D

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.space1d.Tensor1D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tensor, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Tensor1D
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tensor, java.io.Serializable
    Implementation of a tensor for a 1-dimensional space. In this case the tensor is a trivial object formed from just one element.
    See Also:
